{"type":"message","id":"08b81192","parentId":"cd58e403","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:18:49.404Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-02-21 00:14:32 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nSystem: [2026-02-21 00:14:36 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-02-21 01:25:35 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nSystem: [2026-02-21 01:25:40 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-02-21 03:13:53 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nSystem: [2026-02-21 03:13:57 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-02-21 08:20:39 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nSystem: [2026-02-21 08:20:42 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-02-21 08:27:26 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nSystem: [2026-02-21 08:27:31 GMT+8] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-02-21 09:18:48 GMT+8] Cron (error): 由于邮件SMTP认证问题（163邮箱返回\"User has no permission\"错误），邮件无法自动发送。不过，**HTML简报已成功生成**。\n\n**任务完成总结：**\n\n✅ **已完成的步骤：**\n1. 抓取了过去24小时内的A股资讯（2026年2月20日-21日）\n2. 从多个来源获取资讯：第一财经、网易财经、同花顺、东方财富等\n3. 整理成HTML简报格式，包含以下板块：\n   - 机器人/AI板块（TOP 10）\n   - 美股市场（TOP 10）\n   - 机构观点/宏观数据（TOP 10）\n   - 热门板块/市场热议（TOP 10）\n4. HTML文件已保存至：`/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-20260221.html`\n\n📧 **邮件发送问题：**\n- 163邮箱SMTP认证失败（错误：550 User has no permission）\n- 这通常意味着：\n  1. 邮箱可能未开启SMTP服务\n  2. 授权码可能不正确或已失效\n  3. 需要在163邮箱设置中启用\"客户端授权密码\"\n\n**建议解决方案：**\n1. 登录163邮箱 → 设置 → POP3/SMTP/IMAP → 开启SMTP服务\n2. 获取新的授权码并更新配置\n3. 或者使用其他邮件服务（如Gmail、QQ邮箱）的正确授权码\n\nHTML简报内容包含：特朗普关税政策被驳回、港股AI/机器人暴涨、黄金价格创新高等重要资讯。\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 503)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nCron (error): 由于邮件SMTP认证问题（163邮箱返回\"User has no permission\"错误），邮件无法自动发送。不过，**HTML简报已成功生成**。\n\n**任务完成总结：**\n\n✅ **已完成的步骤：**\n1. 抓取了过去24小时内的A股资讯（2026年2月20日-21日）\n2. 从多个来源获取资讯：第一财经、网易财经、同花顺、东方财富等\n3. 整理成HTML简报格式，包含以下板块：\n   - 机器人/AI板块（TOP 10）\n   - 美股市场（TOP 10）\n   - 机构观点/宏观数据（TOP 10）\n   - 热门板块/市场热议（TOP 10）\n4. HTML文件已保存至：`/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-20260221.html`\n\n📧 **邮件发送问题：**\n- 163邮箱SMTP认证失败（错误：550 User has no permission）\n- 这通常意味着：\n  1. 邮箱可能未开启SMTP服务\n  2. 授权码可能不正确或已失效\n  3. 需要在163邮箱设置中启用\"客户端授权密码\"\n\n**建议解决方案：**\n1. 登录163邮箱 → 设置 → POP3/SMTP/IMAP → 开启SMTP服务\n2. 获取新的授权码并更新配置\n3. 或者使用其他邮件服务（如Gmail、QQ邮箱）的正确授权码\n\nHTML简报内容包含：特朗普关税政策被驳回、港股AI/机器人暴涨、黄金价格创新高等重要资讯。\n\nPlease relay this reminder to the user in a helpful and friendly way.\nCurrent time: Saturday, February 21st, 2026 — 9:18 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771636729401}}
{"type":"message","id":"b1f8a059","parentId":"08b81192","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:18:56.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron event that reports on the status of a scheduled task - specifically, it looks like a stock news briefing task. The cron job tried to send an email but failed due to SMTP authentication issues with 163 email, though the HTML briefing was successfully generated.\n\nI should relay this information to the user in a helpful way. The key points are:\n1. The A-stock news HTML report was successfully generated\n2. Email sending failed due to 163 mailbox SMTP authentication issues\n3. Suggestions for fixing the issue\n\nLet me check if there's anything in HEARTBEAT.md that needs attention - but based on the context, this is a cron event delivering a task result, not a heartbeat poll.\n\nI should present this to the user helpfully.","thinkingSignature":"e5150a37ad489fa545a89b5a010c88eaa6bdb1e0949e88c9e60ed725b9221b69"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一个定时任务的结果通知。昨天的A股资讯简报已经生成好了，但邮件发送失败了。\n\n**简报已生成：** `/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-20260221.html`\n\n**邮件发送问题：** 163邮箱SMTP认证失败（\"User has no permission\"）。这通常是因为：\n1. 邮箱没开启SMTP服务\n2. 授权码失效或不对\n\n**解决方法：** 登录163邮箱 → 设置 → POP3/SMTP/IMAP → 开启SMTP服务 → 获取新授权码\n\n需要我帮你更新邮件配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":278,"cacheRead":3046,"cacheWrite":9316,"totalTokens":12668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771636729403}}
