{"type":"message","id":"f908a734","parentId":"9d5f3eac","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:45:22.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No output usually means success. Let me also check the cron job - it was configured to send to qn_home@163.com, but the user originally wanted it sent to nohotnnn@gmail.com based on the memory. Let me check the cron job again and maybe update it.\n\nActually wait, looking at the memory:\n- \"发送到 nohotnnn@gmail.com\"\n\nBut the cron job has:\n- \"to\": \"qn_home@163.com\"\n\nSo the recipient was changed at some point too. Let me confirm what the user wants - they said \"nohotnnn@gmail.com 作为发件人\" but didn't specify the recipient. The current setup has qn_home@163.com as recipient. Let me keep that for now since they didn't ask to change it.\n\nActually let me re-read: \"发送到邮箱 nohotnnn@gmail.com\" - this could mean recipient. Let me check if they want the recipient to also be nohotnnn@gmail.com or keep as qn_home@163.com.\n\nFor now, let me just confirm the msmtp config is updated and test it works.","thinkingSignature":"0f2a52b5f9bd482ac34393ba91f8f989a93653fc76bba3506f13149b38cc3dfe"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 msmtp 配置为 Gmail。测试邮件已发送，检查一下 qn_home@163.com 有没有收到？\n\n另外，cron 任务的收件人目前是 qn_home@163.com，需要改成 nohotnnn@gmail.com 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":12465,"output":283,"cacheRead":11401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771638299320}}
